    psych
Suggests: rjson, RCurl, soiltexture, caret, xgboost, snowfall
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
SystemRequirements: C++11, GDAL (>= 2.0.1), GEOS (>= 3.4.0),
    PROJ (>= 4.8.0)
